text: Traunreut () is a town in southeastern Bavaria, Germany in Traunstein. It is at . Traunreut is in the middle of the Chiemgau region between Munich and Salzburg, about 10 km east of the Chiemsee, 25 km north of the Alps, and 35 km west of Salzburg. ==References== ==Other websites== * Municipality of Traunreut (German) Category:Traunstein (district)
